# The backend API's base URL, including its /api/v1 prefix. Leave unset for
# local dev — the Vite dev-server proxy (see vite.config.ts) forwards relative
# /api/v1 requests to http://localhost:3000. In production (Vercel), set this
# to the deployed backend's URL, e.g.:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL="https://tankha-api.onrender.com/api/v1"
